{"tid":1041634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實而家啲電訊網絡供應商係咪會私自賣客戶嘅電話同個人資料比人？","createTime":"2019-03-01T03:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T05:27:41.000Z","uid":108668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39fe661857f66b91e1d4ea343e717462d6b943db","tid":1041634,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"我有兩張電話咭 <br />\n一張就用咗好多年 CLS嘅電話卡 用嚟打電話WhatsApp 登記啲乜乜柒柒 咁有Cold call打嚟都叫做正常<br />\n<br />\n另外一張都係近期申請 自由鳥電話卡 專門用嚟上網 去旅行買國外數據<br />\n完全冇人知道我呢個電話號碼 我亦都冇比過任何人 淨係得我自己 同自由鳥嗰邊知道<br />\n<br />\n返工無啦啦收到大眾銀行ColdCall電話 講到我個姓氏出嚟<br />\ncut鬼咗佢線之後發現佢係打比我自由鳥嗰張電話咭<br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係自由鳥洩露我個人資料出去 好奇一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098ebb931f5565f9cc29aeb51eb906221f02a87c","tid":1041634,"uid":140516,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"下次收到呢類開名既COLD CALL<br />\n先問咗條友叫咩名 員工證號碼同埋直線電話號碼先<br />\n之後再問佢點拎你D資料 佢SUPPOSE要同你交代返<br />\n不過9成9 COLD CALL狗都會直接CUT你線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325f547fa27a53e3c0fdfe808a3733cbbde34406","tid":1041634,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"你去google完啲野<br />\n轉頭去電話啲app<br />\n就自動彈啲廣告俾你啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d91032f94ebc641841caca50dde2dab6ab0f71","tid":1041634,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098ebb931f5565f9cc29aeb51eb906221f02a87c","tid":1041634,"uid":140516,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"下次收到呢類開名既COLD CALL<br />\n先問咗條友叫咩名 員工證號碼同埋直線電話號碼先<br />\n之後再問佢點拎你D資料 佢SUPPOSE要同你交代返<br />\n不過